{"id":645756,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":5}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"131","ytitle":"","mtitle":"发言","ftitle":"","authors":["肖林"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，我们的农民兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在台上笑容满脸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他有掏不尽的话儿——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在党的十二大兴奋地发言……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业实行了责任制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大地出现金色的季节；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家有余粮，户有存款，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民兄弟登上幸福船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们的农民兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他正从春天里走来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿农民八亿颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为开创新局面正奔向未来!"}]}